## ServiceFlow Tech Stack

### Core Framework
- Next.js 16.2.2 (App Router, Server Components, Server Actions)
- React 19.2.4
- TypeScript 5

### Styling & UI
- Tailwind CSS v4
- shadcn/ui (Base UI components)
- Lucide React (icons)
- tw-animate-css

### Database & ORM
- PostgreSQL 16
- Drizzle ORM 0.45.x
- Drizzle Kit (migrations)
- pg (Node.js PostgreSQL driver)

### Authentication
- Auth.js v5 (next-auth@beta)
- bcryptjs (password hashing)

### Forms & Validation
- React Hook Form 7.x
- Zod v4
- @hookform/resolvers

### Data Visualization
- Recharts 3.x

### Table Management
- TanStack Table v8

### Utilities
- date-fns 4.x
- clsx + tailwind-merge (className utilities)
- sonner (toast notifications)
- tsx (TypeScript execution for seed scripts)

### Dev Tools
- ESLint
- Drizzle Kit (DB management)
